{"tid":1691010,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過表白係想對方拒絕","createTime":"2019-11-03T13:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T02:32:27.000Z","uid":335574,"like":1,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4afec36817e92e126e28a61d264ecd983ed8c0db","tid":1691010,"uid":335574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:13:22.000Z","msg":"話說我早排因為呢場運動識咗一個女仔<br />\n我同佢都幾啱傾<br />\n遊行發夢都有一齊<br />\n但係同佢傾耐咗計<br />\n就知道佢仲有一個月就要返外國讀書<br />\n個刻我聽到之後好唔舒服<br />\n估唔到佢竟然要走&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我個人認為long d一定冇好結果<br />\n我都feel到佢對我有少少感覺<br />\n但係我一定要表白<br />\n同佢講出我心中嘅感受 <br />\n如果唔係嘅話我會內疚一世<br />\n<br />\n咁之後有一晚我同佢表白咗喇<br />\n但係估唔到佢竟然接受咗 <br />\n仲話可以試下long d<br />\n但係之後我同佢講long d真係好辛苦<br />\n我同你表白係想你知道我對你嘅感受<br />\n<br />\n最後係我拒絕咗自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有同佢講話唔好掛住我<br />\n但係佢到而家仲有keep住搵我<br />\n我覺得自己好衰<br />\n而家後悔緊當初應唔應該表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009a207e1d61636b40cb262b11a89f7494e6c5e0","tid":1691010,"uid":182406,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:17:17.000Z","msg":"玩鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"530386453fba6bf8d66e5911f6832ee2fd00e014","tid":1691010,"uid":57634,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:18:03.000Z","msg":"試下啦"},{"pid":"58cb754701a746a868bf02890756e679322e189c","tid":1691010,"uid":60049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:19:55.000Z","msg":"自私"},{"pid":"4367df80cf160bab570968d1aaa43678483ce772","tid":1691010,"uid":292624,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:21:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08af3fe714f943cf266d99ab11d474b204fbc56","tid":1691010,"uid":334717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class